title: The Bunker 001 (2013) (Digital) (Darkness-Empire)
description:
CBR | English | 36 pages

The Bunker #1
Written by Joshua Hale Fialkov
Art by Joe Infurnari

When a group of friends discover that they will each play a role in the apocalypse, the must decide whether to throw their lives away, or to risk the fate of humanity in exchange for their desires. A dark, tense sci-fi thriller from award nominated graphic novellists Joshua Hale Fialkov and Joe Infurnari.
